                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>The United Nations Security Council held its 503rd meeting on September 26 from 3
                    to 7:55 p. m. The Soviet Representative introduced a draft resolution (U.N.
                    document S/1812) condemning United States bombing in Korea; it was similar to
                    the Soviet draft resolution introduced on August 8 and rejected by the Security
                    Council on September 7 (see the editorial notes, <ref target="#pg_546">pages
                        546</ref> and <ref target="#pg_705">705</ref>). For the record of the
                    meeting, see U.N. document S/PV.503.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
